    "Transfer learning uses pre-trained models on large datasets.",
    "Instead of training a model from scratch on a small dataset, the pre-trained model serves as a starting point.",
    "This reduces the data and time required for training and improves downstream tasks.",
    "TL can be supervised, self-supervised, or unsupervised.",
    "In recent years, self-supervised TL has gained more popularity [25]."
